haslog-1.2: A log processing tool for logs in FITTEST format.

haslog-1.2: A log processing tool for logs in FITTEST format.

This is a utility to process logs in FITTEST format. FITTEST is a research project on the testing of Internet applications, currently still on-going. Some of its testing approaches is based on log analysis. The project defines a log format; and this tool is used to do some basic processing on it, such as converting it to a more compact form and exporting to XML.
